    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is mechanically robust, with the critical subframe reinforcement already completed and the rod bearing service documented. Suspension remains tight with crisp turn-in, while the braking system provides firm pedal feel and consistent modulation. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, this M3 demonstrates solid mechanical integrity and performance-ready dynamics for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
