    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, there are minor road-pebble chips on the front fascia and a faint scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seating shows light creasing on the driver's side bolster, but remains supple and free of tears. Every electronic component, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium audio system and heated seats, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the brake pads have 60% life remaining and the tires are at 7/32\" tread depth. The engine idles smoothly and the transmission provides seamless shifts under all load conditions. I have the full service history available for review to ensure complete peace of mind for the next owner.",
